                <p><strong>Scalp Microneedling with Peptides:</strong> Microneedling se scalp mein tiny channels bante hain jinse melanin-boosting peptides aur nutrients directly follicles tak pahunchte hain. Ye natural remedies ki effectiveness ko bhi multiply karta hai.</p>

                <p><strong>LED Phototherapy:</strong> Specific wavelengths of light se melanocyte cells stimulate hote hain. Ye non-invasive hai, painless hai, aur regular sessions se grey hair progression slow hota hai.</p>

